      ## Document page
      
      You can see the history of each document section and collaborate by leaving comments or asking questions.
      All comments and questions that you leave on the document will cause document authors to be notified by email.
      Other document options are available from the document actions menu.

      The Document Collaborators box shows the other collaborators working on this document.
      Click the “+” button to add more people to the document (authors only).
      To mark a user as an author or approver for the document, click the “options” link (authors only).

      Comments and updates can be seen by all collaborators.
